graph TD
    A[Start: Choose Indexing Strategy] --> B{Dimensions < 100?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Tree-based Index<br>KD-tree/Ball-tree]
    B -->|No| D{Memory Constrained?}
    
    D -->|Yes| E{High Update<br>Frequency?}
    D -->|No| F{Accuracy > 99%<br>Required?}
    
    E -->|Yes| G[LSH<br>Fast updates, moderate accuracy]
    E -->|No| H[IVF + Product Quantization<br>Memory efficient]
    
    F -->|Yes| I[Brute Force<br>with GPU acceleration]
    F -->|No| J[HNSW<br>Best general-purpose choice]

    style A fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style B fill:#bbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style D fill:#bbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style E fill:#bbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style F fill:#bbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    
    style C fill:#bfb,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style G fill:#bfb,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style H fill:#bfb,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style I fill:#bfb,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style J fill:#bfb,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    classDef decision fill:#bbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef outcome fill:#bfb,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px;
